==English==

===Etymology===
Blend of English [[magnet]] and [[pulsar]]

===Noun===
'''magnetar'''

#{{star}}: A [[neutron star]] or [[pulsar]] with an extremely powerful [[magnetic field]], especially those on which [[starquake|starquakes]] occur, thought to be the source of some [[gamma-ray burst|gamma-ray bursts]]

